<h5 id="subject_842941">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=90455.msg842941#msg842941" rel="nofollow">【PF官方弹药汇总】2017/03/23</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_842941'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_842941'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2017-03-23, 周四 13:59:42 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_842941_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_842941"><strong>原文来自<a href="http://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/</a></strong><br><hr /><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>书目列表，中文名，缩写和译者</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: Core Rulebook，核心规则，CRB<br>Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: Ultimate Combat，极限格斗，UC<br>Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: Ultimate Intrigue，极限诡道，UI<br>Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: Advanced Race Guide，进阶种族手册，ARG<br>Pathfinder Roleplaying Game: Advanced Player Guide，进阶玩家手册，APG<br>Pathfinder Campaign Setting，战役设定，PCS<br>Pathfinder #15 Second Darkness: The Armageddon Echo ，-， AP#15<br>Pathfinder Player Companion: Elves of Golarion，格拉里昂的精灵，Elves<br>Pathfinder Player Companion: Halflings of Golarion，格拉里昂的半身人，Halflings<br>Pathfinder Player Companion: Alchemy Manual，炼金师手册，AM<br>Pathfinder Player Companion: Adventurer&#039;s Armory，冒险家的武器库，AA<br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=74202.msg700670#msg700670" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">Pathfinder Player Companion: Ranged Tactics Toolbox ，远程战术工具匣，RTT，月夜白雨</a><br>W1 - Conquest Of Bloodsworn Valey，W1-征服血誓者山谷，W1<br></div></div></div><span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>弹药（Ammunition）</strong></span></span><br>投射武器使用弹药，譬如弓用箭矢、弩用弩矢、吹箭使用吹针、投石索和半身人投石杖使用弹丸。当持用弓时，角色能以自由动作挽弓搭箭；而弩和投石索需要相应动作进行装填。一般而言，命中目标后的弹药将损毁或不堪再用，而射失的弹药有50%的概率损毁或遗失。虽然手里剑属于投掷武器，但在决定拿取动作、制造精制品或特殊版本、以及判断投掷后状况时，将其视为弹药处理。<br><span style="color: teal;" class="bbc_color"><strong>【弹药分类】</strong></span><br><a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=90455.msg842956#msg842956" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">简易武器弹药</a><br><a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=90455.msg842984#msg842984" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">军用武器弹药</a><br><a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=90455.msg843012#msg843012" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">异种武器弹药</a><br><a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=90455.msg843032#msg843032" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">特殊投掷武器</a><br><span style="color: teal;" class="bbc_color"><strong>【精制品弹药】</strong></span><br>对于单发弹药来说，精制需要6GP（50发300GP）。精制弹药的增强加值不与投射武器的增强加值相互叠加。精制弹药在使用后彻底损坏。（对于耐用箭Durable Arrow来说则不会）<br><span style="color: teal;" class="bbc_color"><strong>【炼金弹药】</strong></span><br>炼金弹药首次出现在《玩家伴侣：格拉里昂的精灵》，它们被称为炼金箭矢。除非另外提及，这些炼金箭都只会对一次攻击生效，无论是否命中目标。尽管精灵们创造了这些配方，但是任何一个炼金师都可以使用这些配方来制造箭矢或者弩矢。下面表格中带有*的箭矢都是炼金箭矢。<br><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>《炼金术手册》</strong></span>：炼金弹药的效果也可以应用于其他弹药和造成穿刺效果的投掷武器。（例如弩矢，飞镖和手里剑）但是火器弹药无法混合炼金材料，那些不能造成穿刺伤害的弹药也不能应用炼金效果。<br><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">同时炼金术手册中对炼金弹药的规则进行了更新。</span><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 