<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_842956"><span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>简易武器弹药 </strong></span></span><br><br><table class="bbc_table"><tr><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>物品名称</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>价格</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>重量（磅）</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>出处</strong></span></tr><tr><td>弩矢（10）<td>1GP<td>　1<td>CRB</tr><tr><td>强酸弩矢（1）<td>40GP<td>　0.1<td>AP#15</tr><tr><td>卓尔毒矢（1）<td>100GP<td>　0.1<td>AP#15</tr><tr><td>火焰弩矢（1）<td>50GP<td>　0.1<td>AP#15</tr><tr><td>蜂鸣弹丸（10）<td>2GP<td>　5<td>AA</tr><tr><td>投石索弹丸（10）<td>1SP<td>　5<td>CRB</tr><tr><td>毒气弹丸（10）<td>100GP<td>　5<td>PCS</tr><tr><td>吹针（10）<td>5SP<td>　1<td>CRB</tr></table><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>弩矢（Crossbow bolts）</strong></span>：一支弩矢在作为近战武器时属于轻型临时武器，它可以造成与同样型号的匕首相同的伤害（重击倍率×2）。买到的弩矢放在一个可以容纳10支弩矢（连射弩是5支）的木制小匣里。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>强酸弩矢（Acid bolts）</strong></span>：一旦成功命中目标，这支弩矢会造成正常伤害并额外造成1D4点强酸伤害。<br>注意：强酸弩矢不会造成溅射伤害。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">On a successful hit, acid bolts deal normal damage and 1d4 points of additional acid damage.Note: Acid bolts do not cause any splash damage.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>卓尔毒矢（Drow Poison bolts）</strong></span>：任何被卓尔毒矢击中的目标必须通过DC13的强韧豁免否则会被卓尔毒素影响。使用卓尔毒矢不会令使用者有中毒风险。<br>缺陷：这支弩矢的奇特构造会影响弩矢的准度。使用卓尔毒矢时，距离减值翻倍。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Anyone struck by a drow poison bolt must make a DC 13 Fortitude save or become affected by drow poison. Those using drow poison bolts do not risk poisoning themselves.Drawback: The strange tip affects the bolts’ accuracy. Double the range penalties when using a drow poison bolt.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>火焰弩矢（Fire bolts）</strong></span>：一旦成功命中目标，这支弩矢会造成正常伤害并额外造成1D4点火焰伤害。<br>注意：火焰弩矢不会造成溅射伤害，并且火焰不足以点燃目标（除非目标已经变得易燃）<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">On a successful hit, fire bolts deal normal damage plus 1d4 points of fire damage.Note: Alchemical fire bolts do not cause any splash damage, and the fire burst isn’t enough to ignite targets (unless they are particularly flammable).</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>投石索弹丸（Sling bullets）</strong></span>：买到的弹丸放在一个可以容纳10颗弹丸的皮质小袋里。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>蜂鸣弹丸（Groaning bullets）</strong></span>：这些弹丸有着层叠的蜂窝状结构，因此他们飞行时会在500尺范围内发出令人毛骨悚然的声音。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">These sling bullets are honeycombed with overlapping perforations that cause them to emit an eerie moan audible within 500 feet of their flight path.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>毒气弹丸（Smoke bullets）</strong></span>：当这些弹丸撞击了一个目标，他们会爆发释放出充满有害气体的云雾（cloud），被击中的生物需要通过DC13的强韧豁免。如果豁免失败，目标会反胃2轮。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">When they strike a target, they burst, releasing a cloud of noxious gas that requires the creature struck to attempt a DC 13 Fortitude save. If the save fails, the target is nauseated for 2 rounds.<br></div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>吹箭（Blowgun darts）</strong></span>：这只轻薄的飞镖由硬木制成、底端有协助飞行稳定性的羽毛等物，被吹箭筒作为弹药使用。吹镖发射前从反面装填进吹箭筒。</div>
</div>
</div>
