</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_842984"><span style="color: maroon;" class="bbc_color"><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>军用武器弹药</strong></span></span><br><br><table class="bbc_table"><tr><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>物品名称</strong></span>　　　　<td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>价格</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>重量（磅）</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>出处</strong></span>　　<td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>物品名称</strong></span>　　　　<td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>价格</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>重量（磅）</strong></span><td><span style="color: purple;" class="bbc_color"><strong>出处</strong></span></tr><tr><td>箭矢（20）<td>1GP<td>3<td>CRB<td>分叉箭（20）<td>2GP<td>3<td>RTT</tr><tr><td>倒钩箭（20）<td>2GP<td>3<td>RTT<td>圣水箭*（1）<td>30GP<td>-<td>AM</tr><tr><td>流血箭*（1）<td>160GP<td>-<td>AM<td>渐燃箭*（1）<td>100GP<td>-<td>AM</tr><tr><td>钝头箭（20）<td>2GP<td>3<td>APG<td>雾箭（1）<td>10GP<td>-<td>APG</tr><tr><td>耐用箭*（1）<td>1GP<td>-<td>AM<td>破片箭*（1）<td>25GP<td>-<td>AM</tr><tr><td>染色箭*（1）<td>1GP<td>-<td>AM<td>纠缠箭*（1）<td>20GP<td>-<td>AM</tr><tr><td>飞箭（20）<td>2GP<td>3<td>APG<td>蓟花箭（1）<td>1GP<td>0.15<td>AA</tr><tr><td>火箭（20）<td>10GP<td>3<td>RTT<td>掷箭（1）<td>5SP<td>0.5<td>RTT</tr><tr><td>磁石箭*（1）<td>10GP<td>-<td>AM<td>绊足箭*（1）<td>25GP<td>-<td>AM</tr><tr><td>信息箭*（1）<td>15GP<td>-<td>AM<td>响箭（20）<td>2GP<td>3<td>UC</tr><tr><td>竹矢（10）<td>1GP<td>0.5<td>UC<td><td><td><td></tr></table><ul class="bbc_list"><li>没有标注重量的弹药，除非特殊说明，则20发即为3磅<li>部分物品价格与出处根据《炼金术手册》进行了更新<li>表格中带“ * ”的物品为炼金弹药</ul><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>箭矢 Arrows</strong></span><br>一支箭矢在作为近战武器时属于轻型临时武器（攻击检定-4），它可以造成与同样型号的匕首相同的伤害（重击倍率×2）。买到的箭放在一个可以容纳20支箭的皮革箭袋里。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>钝箭 Blunt arrows</strong></span><br>这只箭矢的先端是造成钝击伤害而非穿刺的圆木。射手能够使用钝箭造成非致命伤害（依然由于以致命武器造成非致命伤害而使攻击检定承受-4减值）<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>飞箭 Flight arrows </strong></span><br>这种箭矢的轻杆提供了极远的射程。长弓使用飞箭时的射程增量提高20尺，短弓则提高10尺。它们判断伤害时视为武器型号小于实际一级。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>雾箭 Smoke arrow</strong></span><br>这只箭矢实际上是能够被弓发射的、削尖的烟雾棒。它在飞行时拖曳着烟尘，并在命中之处产生5英尺立方的烟雾。在伤害、射程等其他方面，雾箭的功能和普通箭矢别无二致。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>响箭 Whistling arrows</strong></span><br>响箭具有特殊的箭身穿孔和羽翎，它们可以在被射出后发出极其尖锐而响亮的呼啸声（足以影响半径500尺的范围）。响箭以20支装一壶出售。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>竹矢 Bamboo shaft arrows</strong></span><br>这种长度约一尺的箭矢是袖箭的弹药，竹矢可以作为临时近战武器使用，伤害相当于一副同体型大小的带刺铁手套。袖箭可以一次装填10发竹矢。<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>倒钩箭 Barbed Arrow</strong></span>（在AA中称为Grappling Arrow）<br>倒钩箭的尖端像一个鱼叉。当将倒钩箭尾部连上丝绳然后发射，该次攻击的射程增量会降低为30尺，但此次攻击时武器获得擒抱武器特殊属性。<br>倒钩箭存在弩矢版本。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Arrow/Bolt, Barbed<br>The head of a barbed arrow resembles that of a harpoon.<br>Benefit(s) When a barbed arrow is attached to a length of silk rope and fired from a bow, the arrow’s range increment is reduced to 30 feet, but it gains the grapple special weapon quality.<br>Barbed bolts exist for crossbows.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>火箭 Incendiary Arrow</strong></span><br>火箭上绑着一个金属包，里面装着易燃物质。使用火箭的攻击承受-1罚值。你可以用一个引发借机攻击的全回合动作点燃至多6支火箭（若使用火柴则可以改为标准动作）。点燃后，火箭可以燃烧2轮。用燃烧的火箭命中会额外造成1点火焰伤害。若该次攻击重击成功，则目标必须通过DC15反射豁免，否则会着火。<br>火箭存在弩矢版本。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Arrow/Bolt, Incendiary<br>Benefit(s) You take a –1 penalty on attack rolls when firing incendiary arrows. You can light up to six incendiary arrows as a full-round action (a standard action if you use a tindertwig) that provokes attacks of opportunity. Once lit, the arrow burns for 2 rounds. A lit incendiary arrow deals an additional 1 point of fire damage.On a critical hit, the target must succeed at a DC 15 Reflex save or catch fire.<br>Incendiary bolts exist for crossbows.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>分叉箭 Pronged Arrow</strong></span><br>不同于普通箭矢在箭尖变窄，分叉箭的尖端是如同新月一般的分叉口。这种箭起源于狩猎游戏，分叉箭造成的伤害减小1个体型，但在对比你小至少1个体型的生物或物体进行攻击时获得+1加值。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Arrow, Pronged<br>Rather than narrowing to a single point, a pronged arrow has a wide face with two points resembling a crescent or V-shape.<br>Benefit(s) Originally used for hunting game, a pronged arrow deals damage as if one size category smaller, but you gain a +1 bonus on attack rolls against creatures or objects one or more size categories smaller than you.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>掷箭 Throwing Arrow</strong></span><br>因为太长，掷箭无法用于弓，因此它的尾部也没有弓弦槽。取而代之的是，在箭羽前端有一个V型槽可以用来装载掷箭索。若不使用掷箭索，则将掷箭视为飞镖。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Too long to use in a bow, the throwing arrow has no nock at the tail. Instead, it has a notch ahead of the fletching where a throwing arrow cord can be attached.<br>Benefit(s) If thrown without the use of a cord, treat a throwing arrow as a dart.<br></div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>蓟花箭 Thistle Arrow</strong></span><br>这支由一种有毒植物的花制成的箭，命中后会将该次伤害作为流血效果持续1D6轮。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Thistle Arrow：Crafted from the thistles of a poisonous plant, these barbed arrows deal damage as a bleed effect for 1d6 rounds after a hit.</div></div></div><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>流血箭 Bleeding Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述流血效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>耐用箭 Durable Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述耐用效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>染色箭 Dye Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述染色效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>磁石箭 Lodestone Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述磁石效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>信息箭 Pheromone Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述信息效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>圣水箭 Raining Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述圣水效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>渐燃箭 Slow Burn Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述渐燃效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>破片箭 Splintercloud Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述破片效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>纠缠箭 Tangleshot Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述纠缠效果<br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>绊足箭 Trip Arrow</strong></span><br>通过炼金配方使用普通箭矢制成的炼金武器，它具有上文所述绊足效果</div>
</div>
